<p>I couldn't resist getting out and flying the Frenzy flag in this beautiful weather!</p>
<p>Still, I treated the ride like a "day off", spinning at an average of 144bpm with a high of 154bpm (65-75% capacity) up Flagstaff.  The sky was crystal clear and the views magnificent.  The temps were just right too.</p>
